{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c46220de00","title":"关于首先要把北京、上海、天津的文化革命运动搞好的一段话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"85093625c7","index":0,"year":1967,"month":6,"day":8,"articleId":"c46220de00"}],"tags":[{"id":"c1c0033e04","name":"指导理论","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e139a9746b","name":"城镇居民","type":"主题"},{"id":"e2305b9e63","name":"毛泽东","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d0828dba1b","type":"title","text":"关于首先要把北京、上海、天津的文化革命运动搞好的一段话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c46220de00"},{"id":"1ef4bfdebd","type":"paragraph","text":"中国革命的胜利，主要不是搞地下斗争，而是武装斗争。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c46220de00"},{"id":"400b22f869","type":"paragraph","text":"就是全世界都黑了，只要中国是光明的，那世界就有希望，没什么问题。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c46220de00"},{"id":"ca4e0921d3","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级文化大革命，首先要把北京、上海、天津这几个地方搞好。上海就是工人这个队伍比较好，所以上海的局势中央也比较放心。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c46220de00"}],"page":{"id":"35deae8c72","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c46220de00","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}